additionalProperty.value: Ingredients- Cheddar Cheese 45% (Pasteurised Milk, Salt, Starter Culture, Enzymes (Non Animal Rennet, Non Animal Lipase)), Colby Cheese 45% (Pasteurised Milk, Salt, Starter Culture, Enzyme (Non Animal Rennet), Parmesan Cheese 10% (Pasteurised Milk, Salt, Starter Culture, Enzymes (Non Animal Rennet, Animal Lipase)), Anti-caking Agent (460).

description: All Liddells products are all made from real dairy, lactose free and where needed we add the lactase enzyme to break down the lactose into two simple sugars: glucose and galactose. These sugars can be easily absorbed in the small intestine, keeping your tummy feeling happy. That's all it is!
name: Lactose Free Shredded Pizza Blend
